# 📡 AMOS Communication

## Message Format
```bash
tmux send-keys -t [TARGET] "[FROM]→[TO]: [MESSAGE]" C-m
```

## Common Messages

### Manager
```bash
# Assign work
tmux send-keys -t PLANNER "MANAGER→PLANNER: Plan login system" C-m
tmux send-keys -t WORKER "MANAGER→WORKER: Build login form" C-m

# Check status
tmux send-keys -t WORKER "MANAGER→WORKER: Status update?" C-m
```

### Planner
```bash
# Deliver plan
tmux send-keys -t MANAGER "PLANNER→MANAGER: ✅ Plan ready - 3 tasks" C-m

# Report issue
tmux send-keys -t MANAGER "PLANNER→MANAGER: ⚠️ Need API specs" C-m
```

### Worker
```bash
# Progress
tmux send-keys -t MANAGER "WORKER→MANAGER: 75% - Writing tests" C-m

# Complete
tmux send-keys -t MANAGER "WORKER→MANAGER: ✅ Login form done" C-m

# Blocked
tmux send-keys -t MANAGER "WORKER→MANAGER: ⚠️ Missing config" C-m
```

## Quick Status Icons
- ✅ Complete/Success
- ❌ Failed/Error
- ⚠️ Blocked/Warning
- 🔄 In Progress
- 📌 New Task